txt.en: Strong White Hand Orcs have been spotted on the road in the High Knolls, making travel in Wildermore treacherous for ordinary folk.

'I have received news of Orcs, strong Orcs, patrolling the northern road in the High Knolls. Who do they think they are?\n\n'Only the Free Peoples have leave to travel unhindered in our land. The time of NÃºrzum is over. Orcs may not ride wherever they wish.'
Dudoc is in Forlaw.\n\nYou should speak with Dudoc.
'Are you ready to ride to the High Knolls? The Orcs await your vengeance!'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This is an instanced public questing area.</rgb>
'You have done well, [placeholder]. With the road safe, we can begin to rebuild.'
<rgb=#FF0000>Completing Wildermore's Recovery will cancel this quest.</rgb>
Defeat invaders on the north road ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
The northern road in the High Knolls can be reached by speaking with Dudoc to travel there.\n\nYou should travel to the High Knolls and reclaim the northern road from the Orc invaders.
